{"classData":[{"comment":"/**\n * @module ai/scripts/maintenance/kbPushClient\n *\n * @summary Tenant-side repo-push client for the KB `ingest_source_files` MCP facade.\n *\n * This is the operator-facing invocation primitive for the MCP-over-StreamableHTTP path.\n * Tenant hooks or CI jobs build a content-bearing ingestion envelope, then this\n * client connects to the cloud KB MCP `/mcp` endpoint with an automation identity token\n * and calls `ingest_source_files`. Large backfills remain the co-located\n * `ai:ingest-tenant` bulk CLI; this client intentionally preserves the MCP work-volume\n * gate and fails visibly when the server returns `KB_INGEST_VOLUME_EXCEEDED`.\n *\n * Usage:\n * `npm run ai:kb-push-client -- --url https://kb.example.com/mcp --from-file envelope.json`\n *\n * Environment defaults:\n * - `NEO_KB_MCP_URL` - remote KB MCP endpoint URL.\n * - `NEO_KB_MCP_TRANSPORT` - `streamable-http` (default) or `sse`.\n * - `NEO_KB_INGEST_TOKEN` - bearer token for the repo-push automation identity.\n * - `NEO_KB_TENANT_ID` / `NEO_KB_REPO_SLUG` - optional envelope defaults.\n */","meta":{"filename":"kbPushClient.mjs","lineno":14,"columnno":0,"path":"/Users/Shared/github/neomjs/pages/node_modules/neo.mjs/ai/scripts/maintenance","code":{}},"kind":"module","name":"ai/scripts/maintenance/kbPushClient","summary":"Tenant-side repo-push client for the KB `ingest_source_files` MCP facade.\n\nThis is the operator-facing invocation primitive for the MCP-over-StreamableHTTP path.\nTenant hooks or CI jobs build a content-bearing ingestion envelope, then this\nclient connects to the cloud KB MCP `/mcp` endpoint with an automation identity token\nand calls `ingest_source_files`. Large backfills remain the co-located\n`ai:ingest-tenant` bulk CLI; this client intentionally preserves the MCP work-volume\ngate and fails visibly when the server returns `KB_INGEST_VOLUME_EXCEEDED`.\n\nUsage:\n`npm run ai:kb-push-client -- --url https://kb.example.com/mcp --from-file envelope.json`\n\nEnvironment defaults:\n- `NEO_KB_MCP_URL` - remote KB MCP endpoint URL.\n- `NEO_KB_MCP_TRANSPORT` - `streamable-http` (default) or `sse`.\n- `NEO_KB_INGEST_TOKEN` - bearer token for the repo-push automation identity.\n- `NEO_KB_TENANT_ID` / `NEO_KB_REPO_SLUG` - optional envelope defaults.","longname":"module:ai/scripts/maintenance/kbPushClient","$longname":"ai/scripts/maintenance/kbPushClient","$kind":"module","id":8028,"neoClassName":"Neo.ai.scripts.maintenance.kbPushClient"},{"comment":"/**\n * @summary Creates an isolated Commander parser for one invocation.\n * @returns {Command}\n */","meta":{"range":[1848,3014],"filename":"kbPushClient.mjs","lineno":42,"columnno":0,"path":"/Users/Shared/github/neomjs/pages/node_modules/neo.mjs/ai/scripts/maintenance","code":{"id":"astnode100108967","name":"createArgParser","type":"FunctionDeclaration","paramnames":[]},"vars":{"program":"module:ai/scripts/maintenance/kbPushClient~createArgParser~program","":null}},"summary":"Creates an isolated Commander parser for one invocation.","returns":[{"type":{"names":["Command"]}}],"name":"createArgParser","longname":"module:ai/scripts/maintenance/kbPushClient~createArgParser","kind":"function","scope":"inner","memberof":"module:ai/scripts/maintenance/kbPushClient","params":[],"$longname":"ai/scripts/maintenance/kbPushClient~createArgParser","$kind":"method","id":8029,"neoClassName":"Neo.ai.scripts.maintenance.kbPushClient"},{"comment":"/**\n * @summary Parses the tenant push-client CLI argv.\n * @param {String[]} argv `process.argv.slice(2)`.\n * @param {Object} env Environment defaults; injected by tests.\n * @returns {Object}\n */","meta":{"range":[3212,4380],"filename":"kbPushClient.mjs","lineno":74,"columnno":0,"path":"/Users/Shared/github/neomjs/pages/node_modules/neo.mjs/ai/scripts/maintenance","code":{"id":"astnode100109054","name":"parseArgs","type":"FunctionDeclaration","paramnames":["argv","env"]},"vars":{"program":"module:ai/scripts/maintenance/kbPushClient~parseArgs